headline.print_headline: On Day 2 After Miller's Injury, Buckeyes Moving On
headline.main: On Day 2 After Miller's Injury, Buckeyes Moving On

lead_paragraph: When star quarterback Braxton Miller cried out in pain and crumpled to the ground during No. 5 Ohio State's practice on Monday, coach Urban Meyer wasn't certain what had happened.
